    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very reliable, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that starts right up without issue. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light signs of use, while the exterior paint retains a nice shine despite a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with its age. It drives beautifully and is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs required.",
